  • Constructor Details

    • SwerveBase

      public SwerveBase(GyroIO gyroIO, SwerveModuleIO flIO, SwerveModuleIO frIO, SwerveModuleIO blIO, SwerveModuleIO brIO, double loopPeriodSecs, int[] filterTags, Matrix<N3,N1> trustautostdDev, Matrix<N3,N1> trusttelestdDev, Matrix<N3,N1> regautostdDev, Matrix<N3,N1> regtelestdDev, SwerveConstants constants, com.pathplanner.lib.config.RobotConfig config)
      Core constructor for the swerve base, dont use this unless you know what you are doing
      Parameters:
      gyroIO - the gyro to be used
      flIO - the front left swerve module
      frIO - the front right swerve module
      blIO - the back left swerve module
      brIO - the back right swerve module
      loopPeriodSecs - processor loop period in seconds (default 0.02)
      filterTags - the tags to be ignored by the cameras
      trustautostdDev - the trust std devs for auto
      trusttelestdDev - the trust std devs for tele
      regautostdDev - the regular std devs for auto
      regtelestdDev - the regular std devs for tele
      constants - the constants for the swerve base
